{"tid":2064920,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Yvonne 闊別早辰。早晨三個月後首度主持","createTime":"2020-06-15T07:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T01:15:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d79dc5363c96c51c96036434f2fbaf7283dcbf6f","tid":2064920,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:02:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LBBjsgIW6uA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLBBjsgIW6uA&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8j4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=479303e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LBBjsgIW6uA</a><br />\n<br />\n上周五，警方於多區驅散及拘捕市民，有女學生被防暴警員以壓頭跪頸式拘捕，該學生接受訪問時候表示，對防暴警員的行為感到憤怒及難過，警方強調拘捕過程符合警方武力使用原則。<br />\n<br />\n美國非裔男子弗洛伊德懷疑被警員暴力執法後死亡的事件，觸發新一輪全美平權運動，美國串流影視平台HBO Max 宣布，將電影經典名作《亂世佳人》下架。<br />\n<br />\n《讀字快樂》嘉賓：黃綺琳<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKthismorning/videos/892364261267149/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKthismorning%2Fvideos%2F892364261267149%2F&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8j4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=cbfa10ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKthismorning/videos/892364261267149/</a><br />\n<br />\n早辰．早晨 was live.<br />\n7 hours ago &middot; <br />\nFollowing<br />\n【🕢#早辰早晨☕ 💡Live💡】<br />\n📰#新聞重點🔍 🌏#時事熱話💬<br />\n🚘#交通天氣🌡 💁#手語傳譯🙌<br />\n<br />\n《早辰．早晨》逢星期一至五早上7時30分於港台電視31及facebook直播。<br />\n----------<br />\n🔹香港電台官網: <a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/thismorning\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv%2Fdtt31%2Fprogramme%2Fthismorning&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8j4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=fc661e85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv/dtt31/programme/thismorning</a><br />\n<br />\n🔹Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKthismorning\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKthismorning&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8j4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=6bd8b65e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKthismorning</a>"},{"pid":"5c29b8a666fb975fbbea56b54cc318bec643571d","tid":2064920,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ba4020b965d854e692ab9c11c42439dcf4a2c7","tid":2064920,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b340e208f47a96d5260cae6753c74aac56e4ee","tid":2064920,"uid":229275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:06:24.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcb8d5c0fb205c315d0ef29b26de778bc5fe5c6","tid":2064920,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928aedebadcf6a52904c68d5640c478c92245d24","tid":2064920,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:07:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e21683bbe26a7207e00aed142cce6891afbfaef","tid":2064920,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:07:28.000Z","msg":"易安BB"},{"pid":"3f9442c77c1175f6c06cf9ee3915be6b5630a3a2","tid":2064920,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T07:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oy8Sjjb.gif\" da